    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AApplication
    Abstract class representing a BTO application in the system.
    AAuthenticationController
    Abstract class for Authentication Controller in the BTO Management System.
    ABaseController
    Abstract base class for controllers in the BTO Management System.
    ABaseController.OperationResult
    Class for operation results.
    ABaseController.ResultType
    Enumeration of possible operation result types.
    App
    The App class initiates the BTO Management System startup.
    Applicant
    Class representing an applicant in the BTO Management System.
    ApplicantDataManager
    ApplicantDataManager handles the interaction between the application and the ApplicantList.txt file.
    ApplicantMenuBuilder
    Menu builder for Applicant users.
    Application
    Class representing a BTO application in the system.
    ApplicationController
    Controller for managing BTO applications in the system.
    ApplicationDataManager
    ApplicationDataManager handles the reading and writing of application data to/from the application list file.
    ApplicationStatus
    Enumeration for the status of BTO applications.
    ApplicationView
    View for application-related operations in the BTO Management System.
    AProject
    Abstract class representing a BTO project in the system.
    AProject.FlatTypeInfo
    Inner class to store information about each flat type in the project.
    ARenderView
    The ARenderView class is an abstract class in Java that provides methods for rendering views with borders, delays, input handling, and text formatting.
    AUser
    Abstract class representing a user in the BTO Management System.
    AuthenticationController
    Authentication Controller for the BTO Management System.
    BookingController
    Controller for managing flat bookings in the BTO system.
    DataManager
    DataManager is the base class for all data managers in the BTO Management System.
    EligibilityCheckerService
    Service class for checking eligibility of applicants for BTO flats.
    Enquiry
    The Enquiry class represents an inquiry made by an applicant regarding a BTO project.
    EnquiryController
    Controller for managing enquiries in the BTO Management System.
    EnquiryDataManager
    Data manager for handling enquiry-related operations in the BTO Management System.
    EnquiryEditor
    The EnquiryEditor class manages enquiries for a specific BTO project.
    EnquiryView
    View for enquiry-related operations in the BTO Management System.
    FilePathConfig
    Centralized configuration for file paths used in the BTO Management System.
    FlatType
    Enumeration for the types of flats available in BTO projects.
    HDBManager
    Class representing an HDB Manager in the BTO Management System.
    HDBOfficer
    Class representing an HDB Officer in the BTO Management System.
    IApplicationController
    Interface for Application Controller in the BTO Management System.
    IApplicationManagement
    Interface for managing application operations in the BTO Management System.
    IAuthenticationController
    Interface for Authentication Controller in the BTO Management System.
    IBookingController
    Interface for Booking Controller in the BTO Management System.
    IEnquiryController
    Interface for Enquiry Controller in the BTO Management System.
    IEnquiryManagement
    Interface for managing enquiry operations in the BTO Management System.
    IManagerController
    Interface for Manager Controller in the BTO Management System.
    IProjectController
    Interface for Project Controller in the BTO Management System.
    IProjectManagement
    Interface for managing project operations in the BTO Management System.
    IReportGeneration
    Interface for generating reports in the BTO Management System.
    IUserManagement
    Interface for managing user operations in the BTO Management System.
    LoginView
    LoginView handles the user login interface for the BTO Management System.
    MainMenuView
    MainMenuView provides the main menu interface for the BTO Management System.
    ManagerController
    Controller for managing HDB Manager operations in the BTO system.
    ManagerDataManager
    Data manager for handling HDB Manager data operations.
    ManagerMenuBuilder
    Menu builder for HDB Manager users.
    MenuAction
    Interface on what can be done on the menu view
    MenuBuilder
    Interface for menu builders.
    MenuBuilderFactory
    Factory for creating menu builders based on user role.
    MenuNavigator
    Handles navigation between different views based on menu selections.
    OfficerDataManager
    Data manager for handling HDBOfficer data operations.
    OfficerMenuBuilder
    Menu builder for HDB Officer users.
    PasswordChangeView
    View for changing user password.
    Project
    Class representing a BTO project in the system.
    ProjectController
    Controller for managing BTO projects in the system.
    ProjectDataManager
    Data manager for Project entities in the BTO Management System.
    ProjectView
    View for project-related operations in the BTO Management System.
    Receipt
    Class representing a receipt for a flat booking in the BTO Management System.
    Repliable
    The Repliable is the base class for enquiries in the BTO Management System.
    RepliableEditorInterface
    The RepliableEditorInterface is the interface for enquiry editors in the BTO system.
    Report
    Class representing a report in the BTO Management System.
    Report.ReportEntry
    Inner class representing a single entry in a report.
    ReportView
    View for report generation and viewing in the BTO Management System.
    User
    Class representing a user in the BTO Management System.
    UserRole
    Enumeration for the roles of users in the BTO Management System.
    ViewInterface
    A contract for views in the BTO Management System to implement.
